ong>8月11日</strong>：深水埗遊行（1430楓樹街遊樂場）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">逢星期五，日擺買！減少家庭支出</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d0165052ae101196c88e00053b52512eef015f67","tid":1438473,"uid":271051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:45:56.000Z","msg":"手足繼續努力<br />\n支爆不是夢"},{"pid":"78bbfa27e7dd02e1c1911f46ba462d7c1bb8cad7","tid":1438473,"uid":302917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:50:14.000Z","msg":"大陸而家好多城市物價同香港差唔多，或者淨係平少少<br />\n但基層人工真係可以爭十倍（千幾蚊vs萬零蚊）<br />\n香港生活都咁困難，可想而知大陸嘅中底層生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n離爆煲不遠。不過為免影響行動post都係不推了"},{"pid":"16db15141be58a0be5295c0250b84349347a243b","tid":1438473,"uid":60916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:59:57.000Z","msg":"我老母仲成日話大陸物價好平<br />\n4 5年前去玩都已經覺得唔抵玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c442e7c059da486176fabb14fd44546f9359285","tid":1438473,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T20:11:43.000Z","msg":"狗飯30<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e503f3405c68b2966884ac86ae70879ff3e1d4d","tid":1438473,"uid":142974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T18:13:48.000Z","msg":"樓主入左咩FB 群組？"}]}